{"tid":2290552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：無計劃強制市民使用行蹤程式「安心出行」","createTime":"2020-11-18T05:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T07:31:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"75719e8fdfe3702aec8c650ddd7226f08acae961","tid":2290552,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:39:06.000Z","msg":"薛永恒指無計劃強制市民使用「安心出行」應用程式 <br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒表示，無計劃強制市民下載「安心出行」應用程式，至今已有一萬間公私營場所及全港的士參與，「安心出行」亦成為手機應用程式商店過去幾天下載排名榜首，反映市民對政府抗疫措施的支持，強調程式是便民利民，是自願參與，當局會因時制宜，透過不同措施及工具控制疫情。 <br />\n<br />\n薛永恒指，會按部就班，推動場所參與「安心出行」，只要用家曾到過有確診者去過的地方，程式就會自動發送通知，重申程式紀錄的資料會加密儲存於手機，不會上傳至政府系統，資料在31日後會自行刪除。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366795&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1WZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=9822a475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366795</a>"},{"pid":"65ce28a70c6a7b38ce161a74389262aa4b844338","tid":2290552,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"唔強制市民<br />\n但強制場所<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n語言藝術"},{"pid":"f1d9cccb031e2d4acb0f52beaddd7a0512769d2e","tid":2290552,"uid":193077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65ce28a70c6a7b38ce161a74389262aa4b844338","tid":2290552,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"唔強制市民<br />\n但強制場所<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n語言藝術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔裝就唔畀你入去"},{"pid":"d10fb9e176c2d39d1516de4647e6b1e25c84c37e","tid":2290552,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"過兩個月再睇"},{"pid":"fa55e8a45dbc5b5891255be163673c6d1d81b37f","tid":2290552,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T